Emerald Code has created a REST and JavaScript API to enable easy setup and fully customizable eCommerce through the Hubsoft Platform.
<br><br>
The JavaScript API in particular is quite unique because it enables 100% customization of the look and feel of a Hubsoft-enabled website. Anyone with JavaScript, HTML and CSS skills can quickly setup a store front, lowering your costs of labor and the expertise needed. It can also be hosted anywhere, integrated directly into your existing website.
<br><br>
View <a href="http://api.emeraldcode.com/docs">View Full Documentation</a>
